Tags:
  - 873
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Realise what is present here and now. The sages did so before and still do that
only. Hence they say that it looks as if newly got. Once veiled by ignorance
and later revealed. Reality looks as if newly realised. But it is not new.
